253
00:29:26,909 --> 00:29:29,731
On the other hand, creating a high degree of freedom

254
00:29:29,811 --> 00:29:31,472
had been an important theme for us

255
00:29:31,532 --> 00:29:33,393
since the earliest stages of development.

