00:29:58,041 --> 00:29:59,482
But of course, in a physics simulation,

263
00:29:59,502 --> 00:30:00,962
you have to make this sort of thing possible

264
00:30:00,982 --> 00:30:02,443
in a set of complex and near infinite situations.

