00:50:00,040 --> 00:50:01,600
added together in a sum total.

448
00:50:02,581 --> 00:50:06,842
Action, the field design, and the object.

449
00:50:08,202 --> 00:50:10,763
By multiplying actions with the design of the play field

450
00:50:11,083 --> 00:50:13,124
and the objects placed on it, you

451
00:50:13,164 --> 00:50:15,885
create a situation in which almost anything can occur.

452
00:50:17,216 --> 00:50:21,000
and provide a more dynamic and free gaming experience.

453
00:50:21,661 --> 00:50:24,865
I hope you enjoy the puzzle solving process.

454
00:50:25,705 --> 00:50:29,890
It was our aim to deliver a more active and open-ended play experience.

455
00:50:30,511 --> 00:50:35,636
And I hope players will enjoy coming up with their own unique solutions to the game's puzzles and challenges.

456
00:50:57,441 --> 00:51:15,444
I really want players to relish those moments where you do something and think, oh my gosh,

457
00:51:15,504 --> 00:51:16,045
I'm a genius.

